name: Reebok Twistform Blaze 3.0 Running Shoe Sneakers BD4568 Grey
short_description:
Style meets engineering in the Reebok Twistform Blaze 3.0 Running Shoes for men. The Twistform technique streamlines the look, while transitional waves on the sole propel your efforts past expectations, resulting in a superior training expieriance. Go all day with comfort from the cushioned foam midsole.
3DFuseFrame upper for lightweight support
Low-cut design for freedom of motion at the ankles
Foam compound provides a soft feel underfoot
Enhanced transition waves propel you forward
Strategically placed outsole rubber for increased traction
Midsole paint line focuses on heel support
Outsole geometry for flexibility

name: Reebok Dashhex TR Sneakers BD5036 Navy
short_description:
Who knows what you'll seize today. Maybe some agility drills through the park or a dash to across town. Either way, these style-savvy Dash Hex’s are ready to take on your any-terrain, any-plane movements with 3D Ultralite stable support and foot-flexing hex-patterned traction.

Mesh upper with synthetic overlays for breathability with support
Low-cut design for ankle mobility
3D Ultralite EVA foam midsole for lightweight cushioning and stability
Midsole cradle for stabilizing medial and lateral movements
Low-profile, one-piece mid- to outsole with rubber for traction
Forefoot flex grooves for foot flexibility
Die-cut EVA sockliner for comfort and a heel pull tab for easy on and off

name: Reebok Dashhex TR Sneakers BD5036 Navy
short_description:
Who knows what you'll seize today. Maybe some agility drills through the park or a dash to across town. Either way, these style-savvy Dash Hex’s are ready to take on your any-terrain, any-plane movements with 3D Ultralite stable support and foot-flexing hex-patterned traction.

Mesh upper with synthetic overlays for breathability with support
Low-cut design for ankle mobility
3D Ultralite EVA foam midsole for lightweight cushioning and stability
Midsole cradle for stabilizing medial and lateral movements
Low-profile, one-piece mid- to outsole with rubber for traction
Forefoot flex grooves for foot flexibility
Die-cut EVA sockliner for comfort and a heel pull tab for easy on and off
